    "spell": {
        "name": "Warp Mind",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You scramble a creature's mental faculties and sensory input. The target must attempt a Will saving throw. Regardless of the result of that save, the target is then temporarily immune for 10 minutes. *Warp mind's* effects happen instantly, so *dispel magic* and other effects that counteract spells can't counteract them. However, *wish* rituals and abilities that can remove non-magical effects can still counteract the effects.",
        "subtype": "spell",
